              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Blackstone aims $5 billion</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.altdaily.co/email/images/an-dec-11-1.jpg" alt="Blackstone aims $5 billion" href="https://www.altdaily.co" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Blackstone is <a href="https://pitchbook.com/news/articles/blackstone-targets-5-billion-for-latest-life-sciences-fund" target="_blank">raising</a> $5 billion for its latest life sciences fund, following the $4.6 billion hard cap reached in 2020 with its predecessor. The fund targets late-stage drug development, offering performance-based payouts instead of traditional buyouts. These investments are growing popular as life sciences companies face funding challenges due to high interest rates and depressed valuations. Blackstone, shifting away from early-stage investments, is focusing on late-stage Phase 3 clinical trials.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
