              margin-top: 2px !important;">Sycamore Partners deal</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.altdaily.co/email/images/an-dec-11-2.jpg" alt="Sycamore Partners deal" href="https://www.altdaily.co" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4; filter: blur(5px);">
          Sycamore Partners is reportedly exploring a deal to <a href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/walgreens-jumps-report-talks-private-175854095.html" target="_blank">acquire</a> Walgreens Boots Alliance Inc., which has seen its stock fall two-thirds this year. The news boosted Walgreens’ shares by 28%, marking its largest single-day gain since 1980. The pharmacy giant faces challenges from online retailers and plans to close 1,200 stores after reporting a $3 billion Q4 loss. Sycamore’s history of acquiring struggling retailers like Staples and Belk makes it a potential suitor.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
